dc_title_s: Map of the Pleistocene deposits of a portion of southeastern Wisconsin
dc_description_s: This digital map represents Plate XIV of William C. Alden's 1904 paper: 'The Delevan Lobe of the Lake Michigan Glacier of the Wisconsin stage of glaciation and associated phenomena'. Published by the United States Geological Survey as Professional Paper No. 34: https://doi.org/10.3133/pp34
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived map image held at the University of Wisconsin-Madison.
